1
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:08,798
Walked into Carmel, Indiana heat,

2
00:00:08,948 --> 00:00:12,745
Poke in the back, sugar at my feet.

3
00:00:12,895 --> 00:00:16,693
Kiosk said choose — I said "yes to it
all,"

4
00:00:16,843 --> 00:00:20,641
From tapioca pearls to the weird jelly
ball.

5
00:00:20,791 --> 00:00:24,588
Strawberry, lychee, grass jelly flood,

6
00:00:24,738 --> 00:00:28,536
Red bean sinking like a snack in mud.

7
00:00:28,686 --> 00:00:32,484
Crystal, mango, yogurt surprise,

8
00:00:32,634 --> 00:00:36,432
Kiwi's popping like fire in my eyes.

9
00:00:36,582 --> 00:00:40,379
Twenty-five bucks for a cup so wild,

10
00:00:40,529 --> 00:00:44,327
Texture roulette, like a bouncy child.

11
00:00:44,477 --> 00:00:48,275
Carmel’s finest, chaos in a straw,

12
00:00:48,425 --> 00:00:52,222
A sugar-loaded ride, no rules at all.

13
00:00:52,372 --> 00:00:56,170
Matcha milk foam, blueberry burst,

14
00:00:56,320 --> 00:01:00,118
Peach on top just to make it worse.

15
00:01:00,268 --> 00:01:04,065
Every topping stacked like a dare,

16
00:01:04,215 --> 00:01:08,013
Sip once, now you’re stuck in there.

17
00:01:08,163 --> 00:01:11,961
They ask if I want less ice — nah, full
send,

18
00:01:12,111 --> 00:01:15,908
This drink’s not a vibe, it’s a lifelong
friend.

19
00:01:16,058 --> 00:01:19,856
Sinking in pearls, rising in dreams,

20
00:01:20,006 --> 00:01:23,804
Caffeinated joy, sugar-laced screams.

21
00:01:23,954 --> 00:01:27,752
Twenty-five bucks and a laugh too loud,

22
00:01:27,902 --> 00:01:31,699
Couch in the corner, cup tall and proud.

23
00:01:31,849 --> 00:01:35,647
Dad spots one dirty table,

24
00:01:35,797 --> 00:01:39,595
starts preaching aloud —

25
00:01:39,745 --> 00:01:43,542
“Attention,” he says, “is all that it
takes.”

26
00:01:43,692 --> 00:01:47,490
Like that AI paper, but with bobba and
takes.
